  <brief_title>Micafungin Prevention Study for Fungal Disease in Child Receiving Allogenic Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety in Micafungin Sodium for Prophylaxis Against Invasive Fungal Disease During Neutropenia in Pediatric &amp; Adolescent Patients Undergoing Allogeneic Hematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
