  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients will receive allogeneic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Aspartate transaminase or alanine transaminase level &gt; 5 times UNL

          -  Bilirubin &gt; 2. 5 times UNL

          -  History of allergy, sensitivity, or any serious reaction to an echinocandin

          -  Invasive fungal disease at the time of enrolment

          -  Systemic antifungal therapy within 72 hrs before administration of the first dose of
             study drug

          -  Positive pregnancy test
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
